  U7 chit8-jit8 m7-chai khi3 hou7 sim2-mih8 sin5 kam2-tioh8, Khun-hong siuN7 kong2 chhu3-nih kang-san hiah-toa7 kan-ta pang3-hou7 Hui7-bi2 chit8 e5 lang5 ti7 chhu3-nih bo5 i3-su3, chiu7 koat-jian5 si5-the3 siong-li2 to3-lai5. Tui3 an2-ni Siu3-chhun kap Eng5-chong ia7 long2 to3-lai5. An2-ni Hui7-bi2 iu7-si7 Siu3-chhun e5 gan2-tiong-teng. Khun-hong to3-lai5 bo5 sou2 su7-su7, chia hia thit-tho5, lim hoa7, put-ti put-kak soa3 khi3 Sai3-hoa-lau5 chhap tioh8 chit8 e5 hoe-ki kio3-choe3 Bi2-chu. Sit8-chai7 u7 sui2 kin-ni5 19 hoe3. Na2-chun2 hoe ham5-m5 tu2-a2 khui. Liu2-hioh8-bai5, eng-ko phiN7, tai7-hi5 chhui3, sia7-liu5 khi2, bak8-chiu teng5-sun5, bak8-chiah mng5 tng5-tng5. Bin7-bah hun2-peh8, chhio3 tioh8 siang-peng5 chiu2-khut-a2 chin sui2. Heng koan5, io se3, kha-chhng-tau2 toa7 e5. Chheng7 khi2 koan5-kiah8-a2-e5 kiaN5-lou7 e5 khoan2, m7-si7 Hui7-bi2, Siu3-chhun sou2 toe3 e7 tioh8. In nng7 e5 bat seN-kiaN2 lah, na2-li2 tu3 Bi2-chu e7 tiau5. Khun-hong goan5-lai5 tui3 hong3-su3 i2-au7 chiu7 piN3 choe3 chhai2-hoe-phang chit8 e7 khoaN3 tioh8 noa7 lau5 sou3-chap8-tng7. Chek-khek pau-chhi7, Bi2-chu ia7 tan2 bo5 chit ho7 khoeh, chiu7 phoe5-si2 thiam2-mi7 kau-tiN5. Tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 ti-tu tiN5 hou5-sin5 an2-ni. Chit8 e7 toa3-me5 lian5-lian5 kui2 na7 me5 ia7 m7-chai thang to3-khi3. Siu3-chhun e7 si2 e7 oah8, thong siaN5 jiok thau3-thau3. Chu3-si2 khi3 hou7 i chhoe7 tioh8 ti7 Sai3-hoa-lau5. Tai7-nau7 Sai3-hoa-lau5 be7 tit i seN-si2, ian2 chhut chit8-tiuN5 m7-si7 kau5 ka7-kau5, si7 hoa-tou3-hoa e5 hi3-kek. Chu7-jian5 lau5-chu2 ui7 Bi2-chu, sou2-i2 Siu3-chhun ke-soe bin7 hou7 Bi2-chu jiau3 kui2-na7 khang. Tng loan7 e5 si5 Khun-hong choe3 i ho2-lang5-a2 bo5 ti7-tai7 liu tui3 au7 boe2 mng5 chhut-khi3. Siu3-chhun chiok m7-goan7, sui2-bin7 khi3 hou7 Bi2-chu jiau3 kui2-na7 khang tek-khak siuN7 beh po3-siu5. Kau3-chia Siu3-chhun chha Khun-hong chit8-hoe3 i2-keng 31 lah, khah gau5 chng to m7-tat8-tioh8 Bi2-chu 19 hoe3 e5 sui2. Hui7-bi2 to bian2 kong2 kin-ni5 ia7 26 hoe3 lah, kiaN2 si