  Siu3-chhun khoaN3 Khun-hong be5 Bi2-chu, phoat-hu7 ok-tok8 sim, ke3 chiu7 seN-chhut--lai5. SiuN7 chhut ¡§Hap8-kong pho3 Cho5¡¨(Chiu7-si7 chiong-ke3 chiu7-ke3, Se Siok Khong2-beng5 sang3 Lau5-pi7 khi3 kap Tong Gou5 Sun-khoan5 e5 sio2-moai7 seng5-chhin, an2-ni kap Sun-khoan5 lian5-beng5 lai5 phoa3 Pak Gui7 Cho5 Chho3). Ke3 i2-keng tiaN7-tioh8, chiu7 khng3 Khun-hong chhoa7 Bi2-chu choe3 te7 2 ho7 i5-thai3-thai3, Khun-hong chiok hoaN-hi2, o-lo2 Siu3-chhun bat-su7, sit8-chai7 bat su7. TiaN7 chhut-khi3 chhai3-tiam3 loan7 bo5 the2-thong2 kian3-siau3, koh long7-hui3, na7 oe3 tok8 to3-lai5 tian-to3 si2, m7-tat8-tioh8 chhoa7 jip8--lai5 iau2 khah ho2-mia5. Hoe7-goa7 e5 lang5 4 ho7, 5 ho7 i5-thai3-thai3 ma7 u7, te7 2 ho7, te7 3 ho7 bo5 hi-han2, chiu7 chhoa7 jip8--lai5. Chhoa7--lai5 Siu3-chhun chiu7 ka3 Bi2-chu ju5-chhu2 ju5-chhu2 eng7 ke3-chhek lai5 hai7 Hui7-bi2. Khun-hong, Siu3-chhun, Bi2-chu saN e5 siang7 pang5 siang7 chhng5 chin chhin. Hui7-bi2 kio3 Sou3-lan5-e5 lai5 choe3 phoaN7, chin che7 ni5 to si7 an2-ni ka-ti7 jin7-hun7. Chit8 pai2 khe2-cheh8 kau3 m7-chun2 i siang7-toh chiah8 png7. In saN e5 kun2 hoa7-hoa7 lim-chiu2, toa7-hi5 toa7-bah chiah8 lim. Chhai3-boe2-a2 Hui7-bi2, Sou3-lan5, kap iau2 chit8 e5 kio3-chhui3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 Bak8-ni7-ah choe3-hoe2 chiah8. Bak8-ni7-ah bo5 sin3 Chu2, khoaN3 Siu3-chhun khah ang5, i oa2 Siu3-chhun. TiaN7-tiaN7 tui3 Siu3-chhun, Bi2-chu oh8 oe7. Khi3 sun5 chi2-moai7, tau3 choe3 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang, kong2 si7 lou5-moa5 cha-bou2 la7-kha, gau5 koe3-ke khi3 thop8-oe7. Siu3-chhun, Bi2-chu chiu7 giah8 chau3-pan2 tit8 chau3. Khun-hong chiu7 siau2-sin5-khi3 khi2 chiu7 phah. U7 si5 saN e5 chiah8-png7 kio3 i tiam3 toh piN hia hoat8 kui7, kong2 i la7-kha gau5 koe3-ke. Siu3-chhun ka7 i tim3 bah-kut. Kho2-lian5 ah! Hui7-bi2 sim-lai7 chu7-hin7 chin-chiaN3 si7 Chhi3-a2-lai7 e5 pek-hap8-hoe. Ta-ke khou2-tok8, se3-i5 ia7 bou5-hai7, tiong7-hu ia7 bo5 khoaN3-kou3, kiaN2 ia7 si2. Tui3 hia khi2 m7-chun2 i koh chhut-khi3, kong2 i si7 khi3 koaN7-oe7, koe3-k